Usage: FORMAT SERVER_KILL <format description>
  Controls how server kills appear.

  Valid format characters:
       F          Server killing
       T          Nick of person being killed
       M          The kill comment

See Also:  
  KILL
  SET SHOW_SERVER_KILLS
